{"tid":158050,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"本周MC：幽靈行動荒野奪週銷榜首 Switch銷量保持領先","createTime":"2017-03-16T04:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T12:18:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1e5bf0fb43222e6ac6c956a3f7350a11fb288d","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:01:36.000Z","msg":"昨晚Media Create公開了他們統計的上周（2017年3月6日-3月12日）日本地區實體版遊戲及遊戲硬件銷量數據。《幽靈行動：荒野》以89791份的銷量奪得頭名，《王國之心 HD 1.5+2.5 Remix》售出62770套獲第二，Switch版《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》44483套排第三。硬件方面Switch售出了61998台，保持領跑銷量榜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《地平線：黎明時分》34292套排第四、《1-2-Switch》20746套排第五，《尼爾：機械紀元》20523套排第六，Wii U版《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》17482套排名第七。<br />\n<br />\n另外闖入前十名的遊戲還有長賣的《精靈寶可夢：太陽/月亮》、《勇者鬥惡龍怪獸篇Joker3專家版》以及《超級炸彈人R》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.a9vg.com//2017/03/16/1/ec80f8f53e9ee8e5803f982799a6a9e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.a9vg.com%2F%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F1%2Fec80f8f53e9ee8e5803f982799a6a9e4.png&h=f7902059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.a9vg.com//2017/03/16/1/7e84fa0d4afd631f6c1fadb7c0f99084.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.a9vg.com%2F%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F1%2F7e84fa0d4afd631f6c1fadb7c0f99084.png&h=cd731471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n硬件方面，本月初剛剛發售的新機型任天堂Switch以61998台的銷量繼續領跑銷量榜；標配版PS4賣出了28902台；New3DS LL賣出了18360台；PS Vita賣出8398台；PS4 Pro賣出了6398台。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.a9vg.com//2017/03/16/1/8dda820e35f6c08d6ba8f5e7501371b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.a9vg.com%2F%2F2017%2F03%2F16%2F1%2F8dda820e35f6c08d6ba8f5e7501371b3.png&h=97dcac41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據MC公佈的歷史數據，PS4在日本的總銷量超過了450萬台，其中PS4 Pro的總銷量超過了20萬台。"},{"pid":"d7075d1237b85bfab0a20600221a8ac2312d0492","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346141d6ab3fa0cdf8bae1d4581767ccb5954683","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500f9f04189eb37c578fb9f9e20709a4b562611d","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6695a20a218e0e341d759795ee7e31c21c0545","tid":158050,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"而家家用機銷量真係少過上一代好多, 應講係一代不如一代, WII,PS,XBOX系都係咁.."},{"pid":"72ebc006c0e01678bb51081f392d5fa720071d52","tid":158050,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家家用機銷量真係少過上一代好多, 應講係一代不如一代, WII,PS,XBOX系都係咁..</blockquote><br />\nSwitch係無貨先大跌，睇返之前訪談<br />\n任天堂之前講今個財政年度預計出貨200萬<br />\n上星期已經賣左150萬，佢今個星期全球只係剩返50萬部機未賣，日本有6萬已經係極限(今個星期全球唔知賣左幾多)<br />\n四月之前佢都應該唔會再有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢個芒產能不足，另外一個訪談提過第一批生產的貨工廠都係得300萬個芒，就算應急都係得100萬部可以動用，但新社長作風係睇數好緊的，今個星期已經講左唔會加大出貨量同加快生產，所以四月之前佢應該全球賣唔到300萬部先正常"},{"pid":"e811e2a3939a8e77ade316fc28e158926c2a0fde","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e43d0f9974f726cd88759d79baff39da76b43d6","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49fc23f67e98bc498765ad90ed7e4479c40dba5","tid":158050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}